。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好啦就當你倒完，又無人抹盤。個盤仲有醬，有放埋落堆乾淨盤度。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好啦當你乜都做晒。你走咗，你個位無人抹枱，遲吓啲客又投訴點解無人抹枱。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n真係多謝曬你。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢班人多數大學生"},{"pid":"18d427cd5542d868160099dd365acead07c3fc2e","tid":425350,"uid":38456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T16:54:30.000Z","msg":"社會上一班反智 過虛偽人"},{"pid":"9e2641149dbdcb1446ee54d15f2e5988666ab773","tid":425350,"uid":65530,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T16:54:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5955c535fd65185d0ace7f85f2bb48e10812b086","tid":425350,"uid":38456,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T16:59:27.000Z","msg":"其實關愛座 風氣都係偽善概人做出黎"},{"pid":"669534f424d297944872d0b890fb6ff038b42e48","tid":425350,"uid":131153,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T17:28:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>忙咪自己收 小人輕鬆咪放低<br />\n利申自己都做過 <br />\n覺得忙起上黎有人幫手收會好感激  輕鬆自己應付到 其他人幫手收我都會即刻衝埋去 有啲唔好意思</blockquote><br />\n你後生仔就咁睇 因為收一兩個盤無咩影響 佢照要請人 再加你都唔係靠佢過人世 但如果係啲老野 你成日幫佢收盤 佢地應該可以全部收晒皮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申：會執晒啲野上盤等人易啲收"},{"pid":"ede955aac40a7f8343af7f2a2be222b61af9a71e","tid":425350,"uid":131153,"like":27,"dislike":5,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T17:31:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>自己做過。你地班自己收真係_街。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n自己拎出去，又嫌污糟唔咁倒落垃圾桶。最後盤上面仲有醬，都敢層層疊。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好啦就當你倒完，又無人抹盤。個盤仲有醬，有放埋落堆乾淨盤度。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好啦當你乜都做晒。你走咗，你個位無人抹枱，遲吓啲客又投訴點解無人抹枱。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n真係多謝曬你。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢班人多數大學生</blockquote><br />\n講最尾果句嘅多數係無大學讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你咪唔鋸囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  反正你日後78成機會都係比大學生rule"},{"pid":"f114df69232554b81d2f3a5db64b7eac4fda248d","tid":425350,"uid":144281,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T19:16:31.000Z","msg":"其實有冇人諗過日本m記個種方式呢 又乾淨又衛生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b6b9ed921529e3430439ee7709bc6c8bd3435f9","tid":425350,"uid":55552,"like":3,"dislike":18,"score":-15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T23:29:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>自己做過。你地班自己收真係_街。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n自己拎出去，又嫌污糟唔咁倒落垃圾桶。最後盤上面仲有醬，都敢層層疊。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好啦就當你倒完，又無人抹盤。個盤仲有醬，有放埋落堆乾淨盤度。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好啦當你乜都做晒。你走咗，你個位無人抹枱，遲吓啲客又投訴點解無人抹枱。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n真係多謝曬你。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢班人多數大學生</blockquote><br />\n講最尾果句嘅多數係無大學讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你咪唔鋸囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  反正你日後78成機會都係比大學生rule</blockquote><br />\n人哋講緊好多大學生將canteen收餐盤文化帶入M記，你係到打晒飛機又踩人又剩咁做乜撚嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Btw我鋸你老母呀</span></span>"},{"pid":"68b7c0364bee6bbcb6e5e374061ca6c42e0e3f02","tid":425350,"uid":124910,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T23:44:29.000Z","msg":"無人做清潔就會自己執，有就唔會。<br />\n反正又唔係我出糧比佢，無謂幫M記慳錢，慳左又唔會減價"},{"pid":"f8b067a9adf44a6a801eef1762c7e84c39f2edd0","tid":425350,"uid":55628,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T23:59:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>自己做過。你地班自己收真係_街。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n自己拎出去，又嫌污糟唔咁倒落垃圾桶。最後盤上面仲有醬，都敢層層疊。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好啦就當你倒完，又無人抹盤。個盤仲有醬，有放埋落堆乾淨盤度。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好啦當你乜都做晒。你走咗，你個位無人抹枱，遲吓啲客又投訴點解無人抹枱。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n真係多謝曬你。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢班人多數大學生</blockquote><br />\n講最尾果句嘅多數係無大學讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你咪唔鋸囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  反正你日後78成機會都係比大學生rule</blockquote><br />\n人哋講緊好多大學生將canteen收餐盤文化帶入M記，你係到打晒飛機又踩人又剩咁做乜撚嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Btw我鋸你老母呀</span></span></blockquote><br />\n點解咁都可以估到人哋係冇大學讀嘅呢？"},{"pid":"2f8e9dc2d13e5fb7ba6ce3e0e18e1dd0a43b6c77","tid":425350,"uid":60169,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T00:04:46.000Z","msg":"你執開， 佢就會抄哂樓面班人， 令人失業。<br />\n<br />\n例子就係台灣m記， 叫人幫輕下前線工作人員自已執盤， 轉頭就抄哂執盤班工人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5134e6c61c5bbc62333cb1c0323d475a8371730","tid":425350,"uid":80736,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T00:06:50.000Z","msg":"其實冇人收先收，有人咪等佢收，趕咪唔收，得閒咪收，有咁難明？"},{"pid":"8d18cad7e529f2163d3b21b411ec0090be31f941","tid":425350,"uid":73722,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T00:09:14.000Z","msg":"其實『自律』同『幫商家慳人力資源』兩者之間有無平衡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n感覺上你係香港做前者，班仆街商家佬實發揮到變後者，再串柒柒搭多句『呢D叫商業頭腦』"},{"pid":"68a85a1cfe25f8afa34094098cbcccebc2fcb2d4","tid":425350,"uid":73722,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T00:11:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實『自律』同『幫商家慳人力資源』兩者之間有無平衡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n感覺上你係香港做前者，班仆街商家佬實發揮到變後者，再串柒柒搭多句『呢D叫商業頭腦』</blockquote><br />\n我已經想像到有一日全香港人都自律肯自己收盤，佢地就會炒晒樓面，再每張枱放條毛巾，嫌污糟就自己抹"},{"pid":"6e1ae286aae1dc8e62a3a1ef7fa23a68345814ea","tid":425350,"uid":72489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T01:11:19.000Z","msg":"我通常一個人堂食就會自己收，<br />\n<br />\n但係同fd你自己走去收，<br />\n<br />\n怕d fd覺得你奇怪/其他原因就唔會做。<br />\n<br />\nBTW 而家好少一個人堂食。"},{"pid":"891c23afb78a05ea3f6613bdca1cf9eaa7f90187","tid":425350,"uid":8040,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T01:15:27.000Z","msg":"唔洗收<br />\n<br />\n如果要自己收盤嘅應該要學ikea 或者大學canteen 咁<br />\n請個人專企係度抺盤，分返好d 垃圾"},{"pid":"694b10e22edaefa15e28a3e9e9db6e353e2594c4","tid":425350,"uid":92468,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T01:42:37.000Z","msg":"不嬲食快餐都自己收餐盤，唔只m記<br />\n家教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以由細到大都係"},{"pid":"e19b729a1b50e9fc34a94696c69d203df00649c0","tid":425350,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T01:46:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實『自律』同『幫商家慳人力資源』兩者之間有無平衡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n感覺上你係香港做前者，班仆街商家佬實發揮到變後者，再串柒柒搭多句『呢D叫商業頭腦』</blockquote><br />\n我已經想像到有一日全香港人都自律肯自己收盤，佢地就會炒晒樓面，再每張枱放條毛巾，嫌污糟就自己抹</blockquote><br />\n所以唔能夠照搬西方個套<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n人地連分類都做得好好睇睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e84ce2fa45b543f0cf556aa93e63f7e085b4e878","tid":425350,"uid":6435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T01:48:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實『自律』同『幫商家慳人力資源』兩者之間有無平衡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n感覺上你係香港做前者，班仆街商家佬實發揮到變後者，再串柒柒搭多句『呢D叫商業頭腦』</blockquote><br />\n係外國可能有<br />\n係華人地區你諗都唔使諗"},{"pid":"c913408dcf374fa4efa0afd83321aab5f3acbe85","tid":425350,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T01:51:20.000Z","msg":"算撚數"},{"pid":"cd87444e7a1da6d75f381575a4fecb2e184ddb0e","tid":425350,"uid":30616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T02:03:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/KZanMHPo7hc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FKZanMHPo7hc&d=HpDrtP0sVLmM%2Fld7z82pcW6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=bfe450a6\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/KZanMHPo7hc</a><br />\n之前睇過呢條片 <br />\n又係講啲人唔撚執野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54b83103cb526815085f04eaa62565c359a7c2f5","tid":425350,"uid":43304,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T02:09:13.000Z","msg":"細個做過M記<br />\n每更有個位置係專負責出floor 執盤, 清潔<br />\n經理見到個客自己擺盤會走黎鬧<br />\n啲茄汁佢地會塔到周圍痴住好污糟"},{"pid":"76f393f8cc27d2f83b0d2877b2cb5114c8ae8376","tid":425350,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T02:26:08.000Z","msg":"點解本應自己收?<br />\n+1 服務費 tips係本應有？"},{"pid":"be7113159f3a3c676f7534373c8cec6eef86b665","tid":425350,"uid":131153,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T02:27:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>自己做過。你地班自己收真係_街。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n自己拎出去，又嫌污糟唔咁倒落垃圾桶。最後盤上面仲有醬，都敢層層疊。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好啦就當你倒完，又無人抹盤。個盤仲有醬，有放埋落堆乾淨盤度。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好啦當你乜都做晒。你走咗，你個位無人抹枱，遲吓啲客又投訴點解無人抹枱。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n真係多謝曬你。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢班人多數大學生</blockquote><br />\n講最尾果句嘅多數係無大學讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你咪唔鋸囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  反正你日後78成機會都係比大學生rule</blockquote><br />\n人哋講緊好多大學生將canteen收餐盤文化帶入M記，你係到打晒飛機又踩人又剩咁做乜撚嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Btw我鋸你老母呀</span></span></blockquote><br />\n首先收盤文化係外國快餐帶起先嘅唔係大學 <br />\n其次佢最尾果句咩用意我諗唔洗讀大學都會get到 就係想一碌鳩屌柒大學生 唔好同我講佢話係多數唔係全部呢啲廢話頭盔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你呢啲人我做pt見証好多 串人係大學生 真係唔明點解讀書多過佢都要比佢串<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b145b70fb1b30e47e90bbb572312de68c064e94d","tid":425350,"uid":14607,"like":27,"dislike":2,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T02:35:03.000Z","msg":"去酒樓飲茶會唔會自己執埋枱啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咪撚同我講飲茶有加一<br />\n茶記夠冇加一啦<br />\n