e":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T04:34:51.000Z","msg":"所謂執盤咪又係係個station到疊高佢<br />\n啲呀姐變相又要倒番啲垃圾 又要抹盤 仲要去番你原本個位到抹枱仲走多轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個個盤都有醬你又疊高就多得你唔少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋啲呀姐驚經理見到啲客執而你唔執姐係無做野 會比人炒 長遠黎講低下階層會唔會無野做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3e09c1d6ed7c03a8735d12a0174929a1d9e77cf","tid":425350,"uid":14867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T04:35:57.000Z","msg":"試過幫手執完個姐姐比人鬧，以後都唔會再幫"},{"pid":"d90ad963814978b25b91b0decc6eca47436a5315","tid":425350,"uid":43190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T04:36:22.000Z","msg":"其實香港老麥根撚本唔想你地自己執<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搞咁多野做乜柒"},{"pid":"ec91d1227b5a10b34cc8f35b153843f2da22eff5","tid":425350,"uid":124277,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T04:36:23.000Z","msg":"扮撚晒上等人真係好撚on9<br />\n不如你自已執埋餐, 抹埋枱啦"},{"pid":"bad05ff0623f1cb22057c7c30e542caa4ae117f8","tid":425350,"uid":12827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T04:36:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你執開， 佢就會抄哂樓面班人， 令人失業。<br />\n<br />\n例子就係台灣m記， 叫人幫輕下前線工作人員自已執盤， 轉頭就抄哂執盤班工人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n美國m記都係咁<br />\n最初就係美國fd叫我唔好執<br />\n根本係呃你d 大愛撚幫佢節省人手<br />\n<br />\n利申：逼到有人等會執，唔係就疊好算"},{"pid":"72ceac0584c6cf84b200234b348076cf42d713c1","tid":425350,"uid":14044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T04:38:31.000Z","msg":"仲要超級市場啲車用完都應該推返去擺車個位<br />\n成日塞到門口全部都係車 唔知點行 on99"},{"pid":"45f9cc69978ef0bd37a33cbb40ccf71099afbc09","tid":425350,"uid":52048,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T04:40:35.000Z","msg":"on9 除非所有餐即刻平$10 我就會自己執<br />\n根本D收費本身就包左清潔既成本<br />\n你自己去執咪益左商家佬"},{"pid":"625dd80420dce88c70f0c5bb8c735dc4194ecdb8","tid":425350,"uid":28279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T04:42:09.000Z","msg":"啲仆街阿姐係要執盤既時候先會係咁咦抹下張枱，你班仆街又齋執盤唔抹，搞到張張枱都係污糟躐蹋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係執就同我奶乾淨佢"},{"pid":"8f1dee49eab5a461ffee8f2356ebba9273c96d7a","tid":425350,"uid":12827,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T04:43:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去酒樓飲茶會唔會自己執埋枱啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咪撚同我講飲茶有加一<br />\n茶記夠冇加一啦<br />\n你班柒頭皮會唔會執埋碗先走啊？<br />\n放入個桶到咋喎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好輕鬆咋喎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 幫到人喎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n執盤只係為左滿足你地自己所謂「幫到人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」、「我有良好美德<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」、「你睇下我會幫手執盤好有手尾啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」既自我滿足感<br />\n好撚虛偽啊屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n不能同意更多<br />\n茶記就咁倒落桶唔怕咩有醬呀，垃圾分類果d<br />\n做咩咁有公德心果班人唔做埋？"},{"pid":"c54abc4ef8e78918f574200b0c7c2fd0f3471f7a","tid":425350,"uid":60376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T04:47:29.000Z","msg":"引入無問題 你炒左班阿姐 咁唔該減價先<br />\n好似ikea咁講明自己執賣平d俾你<br />\n絕對有分加"},{"pid":"2e81d659dfd6076a0555691c086bde0626fcf70b","tid":425350,"uid":14739,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T04:48:03.000Z","msg":"根本香港文化冇呢一飯<br />\n你夾硬要人地執做乜野？？？"},{"pid":"4e6d1074f253399b040840ab87e1da7b9b0b2108","tid":425350,"uid":44211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T04:49:39.000Z","msg":"中資 + 咁做會令佢可以炒緊幾個人，不了<br />\n至多食完會pack好，放返晒d垃圾落餐盤範圍內"},{"pid":"7ac0d2b5a862ec8a7728fec7e69b328485936453","tid":425350,"uid":64481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T04:50:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實有冇人諗過日本m記個種方式呢 又乾淨又衛生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nm記無留意但kfc個放盤位大香港3倍左右,有5定6個隆教你邊樣野放入邊個隆。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n掉杯野飲都分三個窿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dbe2068aa2b318713056d2957c1298509d72402","tid":425350,"uid":2059,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T05:00:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>見過大家樂丫姐大叫<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>[你唔識架啦,放返低等我黎]</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n佢地自己有套方法方便自己,<br />\n唔想人越幫越忘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n根本就係<br />\nd人拎M記同大學canteen比?<br />\n<br />\n大學canteen有個位專係for收餐盤, 亦有個人棟係到負責清潔+處理餐盤<br />\n一係就有架車仔俾你擺係上面<br />\nm記得個垃圾桶上面, 玩層層疊??"},{"pid":"a806ad3fa8fe4137dcc3bfcfa6251a6bd2410b81","tid":425350,"uid":10044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T05:03:10.000Z","msg":"自己收野係一種文化應該方便人地<br />\n請人清潔唔應該因爲咁而cut"},{"pid":"936f0e795ba6bcc3e90f1c9fa569fc2881c01bdd","tid":425350,"uid":33651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T05:04:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一定唔執</blockquote>"},{"pid":"184bc0400e3dadaf8e570e6dced74e052fe8934b","tid":425350,"uid":8572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T05:05:04.000Z","msg":"個餐包埋執台架 執佢老母"},{"pid":"360d144edb0baa7d0a181cc931af1d90fd14d4ed","tid":425350,"uid":120501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T05:08:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>m記咁撚多廢老 佢地一定唔會自己收</blockquote><br />\n啲廢老凈坐邊會食嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f71dd71bcd369973c90412f855495fb490203ac","tid":425350,"uid":72489,"like":2,"dislike":8,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2